data.description: PICTURESQUE 14.6 ACRE FAMILY HORSE FARM! Located just minutes away from beautiful historic Madison Ga, named one of USA's most beautiful small towns by Architectural Digest. The living here is quaint, private, peaceful yet convenient to local interstates and nearby outlying small towns.  Entering through the private gated entrance, the long tree-lined and fence-framed driveway allows you beautiful views of the horses grazing in the front pastures as you approach this magnificent 5 bedroom two-story home, which overlooks the rear and side pastures and the barn. There is tree-lined privacy along the back property line as well as a regulation size LIGHTED dressage/riding arena. Featuring a NEW roof, NEWLY-PAINTED exterior, NEW (2y) HVAC, NEW well filter, this lovingly cared-for home has so many features to love including: Open floor-plan, two-story great room with windows all along rear of home (beautiful barn and pasture views!), keeping room with fireplace off kitchen, gorgeous Brazilian cherry floors, large kitchen with granite breakfast bar on two-sides, mudroom/laundry room, formal dining room with lots of light, built-in bookcases framing the fireplace in family room, a charming home office with views of pasture, large master bedroom with fireplace and views of pasture, large spa-like master bath with walk-in closets, all on main level! On second level are three additional bedrooms with full bath and a media/theater/family room, functional as additional BR if needed. From the charming front sitting porch to the rear entertaining deck, there are pasture views all around. The FULL BASEMENT is stubbed for five rooms and features a FULL FINISHED BATH and walk-out patio. The custom 30x48 barn features six stalls, tack room, wash rack, concrete center aisle, solid stall boards, quality doors and hardware; there are two exterior stalls under-canopy of the 11x48 lean-to which also provides plenty of storage. There are FIVE PASTURES cross-fenced, water access to all, elec fenced top-wire, and the amazing 20x60M LIGHTED RIDING ARENA, NEWLY-RE-SANDED and ready to ride. This property is also INCOME-PRODUCING with several established low-maintenance boarders! Located just outside Madison GA and Monticello GA (10-15 min either direction), this lovely rural town of Newborn is quaint, picturesque, located amongst horse farms and wedding venues, and feels " a world away," yet with interstate access Hartsfield Jackson International Airport is less than an hour drive, as are metro amenities, ideal for those craving the rural vibe yet needing to have airport access for business. The acreage is zoned Conservation/ag use for a lower tax-base, there is a well on property and amazingly low electric bills. Peaceful and private, this well-maintained home and property is move-in ready for your family, pets, and horses.
